"root. In addition, we are assuming that you have setup a ZFS storage pool as "
"described in [Chapter 2](02-zfs_setup). You can use a different storage pool "
"if you have chosen not to use ZFS, but you will need to make adjustments to "
"the initialization questions and answers."
