"If you are interested in clustering, do some additional research on that "
"[here](https://linuxcontainers.org/lxd/docs/master/clustering/)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block
#: ../src/docs/books/lxd_server/03-lxdinit.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Do you want to configure a new storage pool? (yes/no) [default=yes]:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/books/lxd_server/03-lxdinit.md:38
msgid ""
"This may seem counter-intuitive, since we have already created our ZFS pool, "
"but it will be resolved in a later question. Accept the default."
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block
#: ../src/docs/books/lxd_server/03-lxdinit.md:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "Name of the new storage pool [default=default]: storage\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/books/lxd_server/03-lxdinit.md:44
msgid ""
"You could leave this as default if you wanted to, but we have chosen to use "
"the same name we gave our ZFS pool."
